name: MusicRING
description:
MusicRING is an audio visualization tool that supports local files in various formats [eg. mp3, wav, ogg, m4a] and music directly from soundcloud via the track link. 
You will find all the settings by hovering with the mouse on the top left and clicking on the sidebar button and there you will find all the settings [the sidebar is visible by default].
Soundcloud compatibility might be limited [it might stop working at some point and you'll need to wait for it to work again], but local file compatibility is always supported.
